    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver that won't break the bank? This car is a fantastic choice for anyone needing reliable transportation! While it shows some honest character and wear from its time on the road, it remains a solid, functional vehicle that's ready to take you on your next adventure. It\u2019s a great opportunity to get into a steady ride at a fair price!",
